<db:para>Release managers, translators, and developers can use Qt tools to translate Qt C++ and Qt Quick applications into local languages.</db:para>
<db:para>In addition to the Qt translation file (TS) format, <db:emphasis>Qt Linguist</db:emphasis> and <db:code>lupdate</db:code> support XML Localization Interchange File Format (XLIFF).</db:para>
